# Relaciones clave

```
users ──────────────────────────────── refresh_tokens
users ──────────────────────────────── social_accounts (fase posterior)
users ↔ enterprises                 ── enterprise_user (membresías activas)
enterprises ────────────────────────── invitations (pendientes)
workspaces  ────────────────────────── invitations (pendientes)

enterprises ── subscriptions ── plans
subscriptions ── subscription_usage

workspaces (ltree path) ──── jerarquía anidada
workspaces ── workspace_roles (seeded al crear) ── workspace_role_permissions
workspaces ── workspace_user ── workspace_roles
workspaces ── assets ── media (Spatie)
assets ── asset_references (otros workspaces)

workspaces ── rooms ── room_participants
rooms ── conversations ── messages ── message_attachments ── assets
conversations (private) ── conversation_participants ── room_participants
rooms ── streams

todo ── activity_logs
```
